0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: </em>\u0110\u1ee9c vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1eddi gian: </em>21h ng\u00e0y 27/6<br>\r\n<em>\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: </em>S\u00e2n Kazan Arena<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\nTLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>\u0110\u1ee9c 0.81*0:1 3/4*-0.87 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c<br>\r\n<em>TBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>Nhi\u1ec1u 0.80*3*-0.88 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, soi k\u00e8o, t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n chuy\u00ean gia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, soi k\u00e8o, t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n chuy\u00ean gia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/nhan-dinh-duc-vs-han-quoc-va-du-doan-soi-keo-han-quoc-vs-duc.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 21h ng\u00e0y 27/6</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn thua Mexico, \u0110\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 l\u00f9i s\u00e2u v\u00e0 ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, \u201cNh\u1eefng c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng\u201d \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi t\u1eadn nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. H\u1ecd \u00edt nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y nhi\u1ec1u nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh v\u00e0 s\u1ed1c v\u00e1c h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9c ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi 76%, kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ngay c\u1ea3 khi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 10 ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u00fac ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u khi nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng xoay chuy\u1ec3n th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Marco Reus v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Toni Kroos \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chat thep de Duc hoi sinh\" title=\"Ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u1ed3i sinh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Chat-thep-de-Duc-hoi-sinh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ee9c ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1eafng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 2-1 \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang \u1edf trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ef1 tin. 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9 mu\u1ed9n m\u00e0ng. Ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Die Mannschaft gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp n\u1ebfu \u1edf tr\u1eadn c\u00f9ng gi\u1edd, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0110\u1ee9c mu\u1ed1n t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf khi ph\u00e2n chia th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng F. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 r\u1ee5t r\u00e8 n\u00e0o xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH Bang F\" title=\"BXH Bang F\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/BXH-Bang-F.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ee9c hi\u1ec7n x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng F</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng ph\u00e1 khung th\u00e0nh H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c li\u00ean t\u1ee5c v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn. Tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t hay trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00f3ng l\u0103n. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n do Joachim Loew d\u1eabn d\u1eaft th\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ec7m c\u1eadn t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i gi\u00fap h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Marco Reus \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t cho \u0110\u1ee9c. Trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a HLV Loew, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Dortmund l\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t. Anh t\u1ecf ra \u0103n \u00fd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u0169i c\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 Timo Werner hay Thomas Muller, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng n\u00e9t m\u1edbi tr\u00ean ti\u1ec1n tuy\u1ebfn \u201cNh\u1eefng c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marco Reus cua Duc\" title=\"Marco Reus cua Duc\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/Marco-Reus-cua-Duc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Reus gi\u00fap ti\u1ec1n tuy\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Werner v\u00e0 Muller \u0111\u00fang ra l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho danh hi\u1ec7u Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi song \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o. Werner t\u1eebng chia s\u1ebb chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0110\u1ee9c quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n vi\u1ec7c ai l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng tin ch\u1eafc b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y Werner, Muller r\u1ed3i Gomez ghi b\u00e0n. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf r\u1eb1ng \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh, \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd chinh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. V\u00e0 g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 Die Mannschaft l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n hay Mexico, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u00fd ch\u00ed qu\u1eadt c\u01b0\u1eddng, song tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f2n h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf. \u0110\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m, s\u1ef1 chu\u1ec7ch cho\u1ea1c trong c\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 kim chi v\u00e0 3 b\u00e0n thua sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua v\u1eabn c\u00f2n l\u00e0 may m\u1eafn v\u1edbi h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Han Quoc vs Mexico\" title=\"Han Quoc vs Mexico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/Han-Quoc-vs-Mexico.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n2 tr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n ngay v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i khi l\u1ea1i gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 tinh th\u1ea7n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn, Son Heung-min h\u1ee9a gi\u00fap H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c lo\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c th\u00f4ng qua m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi tin, c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd b\u1ecb t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng. V\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n v\u1ea5n v\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n \u0111i hay \u1edf. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf n\u01a1i h\u1eadu ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khai th\u00e1c. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, hai c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00e2ng l\u00ean r\u1ea5t cao v\u00e0 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho hai m\u0169i khoan ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 Hwang Hee-Chan v\u00e0 Son Heung-Min xuy\u00ean ph\u00e1. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng d\u1eabn ch\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7y thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Kazana Arena s\u1ebd c\u00f3 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t l\u00f4i cu\u1ed1n. C\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c 3 tr\u00f2n m\u00e0 gi\u1edbi d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1eb7t ra v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng xem ra s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ecb x\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed5.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nL\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (t\u1eeb 3 tr\u1edf l\u00ean)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: <strong>\u0110\u1ee9c th\u1eafng 3-1</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ly (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"633","checkdouble":"189718"},{"date":"10:49 27/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 19h00 ng\u00e0y 27/6 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nhan-dinh-ha-noi-vs-quang-nam-19h00-ngay-276-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 27/6 (V\u00f2ng 16 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 19h00 ng\u00e0y 276 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 19h00 ng\u00e0y 276 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/ha-noi-vs-quang-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam: 2-2<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh so v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a V-League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. Kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 t\u1ea1o ra v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean BXH sau 15 v\u00f2ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh thua ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua, kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y \u00edt nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean sau v\u00f2ng 16 (\u0111\u00fang l\u00e0 FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 hai nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec3m Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, 25 \u0111i\u1ec3m).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1edfi v\u1eady H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC \u0111ang tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch V-League s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t, gi\u00e0nh s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n d\u01b0\u1edbi quy\u1ec1n HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam \u0111ang c\u00f3 38 \u0111i\u1ec3m, k\u00e9m m\u1ed1c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch (45) \u1edf nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 7 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQu\u1ea3ng Nam l\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 V-League nh\u01b0ng m\u00f9a n\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt. 4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Tam K\u1ef3 ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1 v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng s\u1edbm c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i r\u01a1i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 21 \u0111i\u1ec3m, t\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng 8 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 chuy\u00ean gia \u0111ang tin r\u1eb1ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC s\u1ebd \"nh\u01b0\u1eddng\" Qu\u1ea3ng Nam trong 90 ph\u00fat b\u00f3ng l\u0103n s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn thua S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 2-5 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\nH\u00e0 N\u1ed9i: Minh Long; V\u0103n H\u1eadu, V\u0103n Ki\u00ean, Th\u00e0nh Chung, Duy M\u1ea1nh, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ea1i, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Moses, Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, Oseni.<br>\r\nQu\u1ea3ng Nam: V\u0103n C\u01b0\u1eddng; V\u0103n H\u1ecdc, T\u1ea5n Sinh, Thiago, V\u0103n Phong, \u0110\u00ecnh Th\u1eafng, Than H\u01b0ng, Thanh Trung, Quang Huy, Huy H\u00f9ng, Douglas.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"632","checkdouble":"189719"},{"date":"11:06 27/06","title":"Joachim Low ra chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/joachim-low-ra-chien-thuat-truoc-tran-gap-han-quoc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Joachim Low ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. N\u1ebfu h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00f2a/thua ho\u1eb7c s\u1edf h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i k\u00e9m h\u01a1n, nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Joachim Low. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd theo d\u00f5i th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn Mexico vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng v\u1ebd ra c\u00e1c k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi 2 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau &ndash; chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\"><br>\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Joachim Low ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c\" title=\"Low\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/joachim-low-ra-chien-thuat-truoc-tran-gap-han-quoc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Joachim Low&nbsp;ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Nh\u1eefng c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng s\u1ebd thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng Sebatian Rudy, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb g\u00e3y m\u0169i trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, Jerome Boateng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 v\u00ec chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf, trong khi Mats Hummels b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng Draxler, Muller, Khedira hay Ozil c\u0169ng \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft b\u00e0i to\u00e1n n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t ph\u1ea1t c\u00f4ng khi m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng, d\u00f9 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed7i Son Heung Min, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t gi\u1ecfi khi ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;H\u1ecd r\u1ea5t th\u00edch \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c ch\u1ea1y v\u00e0 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn so v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1edf h\u1eefu 3-4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9. N\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i l\u1edbn. C\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c v\u1edbi Son v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Joachim Low ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cuc-dien-bang-f-truoc-vong-dau-cuoi-tu-than-goi-ten-ai-421-189382.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/cuc-dien-bang-f-truoc-vong-dau-cuoi-tu-than-goi-ten-ai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cuc-dien-bang-f-truoc-vong-dau-cuoi-tu-than-goi-ten-ai-421-189382.html\">C\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng F tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i: T\u1eed th\u1ea7n g\u1ecdi t\u00ean ai?</span><br>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u1ebd trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup, r\u1ea5t hi\u1ebfm khi n\u00e0o t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u1ea1i r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-duc-vs-han-quoc-va-du-doan-soi-keo-han-quoc-vs-duc-421-189718.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nhan-dinh-duc-vs-han-quoc-va-du-doan-soi-keo-han-quoc-vs-duc.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-duc-vs-han-quoc-va-du-doan-soi-keo-han-quoc-vs-duc-421-189718.html\">Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u00f4i s\u1ee5c cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi 90 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/werner-phat-bieu-ve-dt-duc-va-viec-ghi-ban-421-189546.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/werner-phat-bieu-ve-dt-duc-va-viec-ghi-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/werner-phat-bieu-ve-dt-duc-va-viec-ghi-ban-421-189546.html\">V\u00ec l\u00fd do n\u00e0y, trung phong \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng m\u00e0ng chuy\u1ec7n ghi b\u00e0n</span><br>\r\nTimo Werner ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n &ldquo;Nh\u1eefng c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng&rdquo; gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ghi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"631","checkdouble":"189720"},{"date":"11:28 27/06","title":"\"Lukaku gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t con th\u00fa\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/lukaku-giong-nhu-mot-con-thu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn b\u1ea3ng G, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111ang r\u1ea5t coi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Romelu Lukaku. Theo \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Rashford so s\u00e1nh Lukaku v\u1edbi Ronaldo.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Rashford ca ng\u1ee3i Lukaku</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ea1 m\u00e0n b\u1ea3ng G, Tam S\u01b0 s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n chia th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Marcus Rashford &ndash; ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra e ng\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c Romelu Lukaku. L\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Man United, v\u00ec v\u1eady Rashford hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00e0n anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 2 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup, Big Rom \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi, b\u1eb1ng Ronaldo v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m Harry Kane. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ghi t\u1edbi 27 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, Rashford cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con th\u00fa. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, Lukaku l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ed1i \u0111e d\u1ecda l\u1edbn v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, anh \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Th\u00fa th\u1ef1c, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd c\u1ee7a Lukaku, b\u1edfi anh \u1ea5y x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang c\u00f3. Khi b\u1ea1n nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Lukaku, nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9, b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y anh \u1ea5y ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec Cristiano Ronaldo.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rashford so s\u00e1nh Lukaku v\u1edbi Ronaldo\" title=\"Rashford so s\u00e1nh Lukaku v\u1edbi Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/lukaku-giong-nhu-mot-con-thu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rashford so s\u00e1nh Lukaku v\u1edbi Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i M.U, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f9ng nhau \u1edf l\u1ea1i sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c. Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea3 ng\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, anh \u1ea5y \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f9a c\u1ee3t \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, Lukaku l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3&rdquo; &ndash; Rashford chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Rashford so s\u00e1nh Lukaku v\u1edbi Ronaldo, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i l\u1edbn trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eaft c\u00e1, v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Roberto Martinez cho ngh\u1ec9. Hi\u1ec7n nay, c\u1ea3 \u0110T Anh l\u1eabn B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/southgate-khang-dinh-se-quyet-chien-voi-dt-bi-421-189708.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/18/southgate-khang-dinh-se-quyet-chien-voi-dt-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/southgate-khang-dinh-se-quyet-chien-voi-dt-bi-421-189708.html\">Tam S\u01b0 s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng G World Cup, HLV Gareth Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng, \u00f4ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng toan t\u00ednh v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i h\u1ea1ng chung cu\u1ed9c.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/carragher-dt-can-bop-nat-bi-o-tran-dau-toi-469-189525.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/carragher-dt-can-bop-nat-bi-o-tran-dau-toi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/carragher-dt-can-bop-nat-bi-o-tran-dau-toi-469-189525.html\">Carragher: \u0110T Anh c\u1ea7n b\u00f3p n\u00e1t B\u1ec9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nTheo c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Jamie Carragher, \u0110T Anh n\u00ean b\u1ecf qua nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-anh-thach-thuc-ngoi-no-lukaku-trong-tran-chien-voi-bi-421-189527.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/nguoi-anh-thach-thuc-ngoi-no-lukaku-trong-tran-chien-voi-bi.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-anh-thach-thuc-ngoi-no-lukaku-trong-tran-chien-voi-bi-421-189527.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c ng\u00f2i n\u1ed5 Lukaku trong tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7 John Stones ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 \u1edf Everton trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Anh vs B\u1ec9 ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"630","checkdouble":"189722"},{"date":"11:49 27/06","title":"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y 27/6: Messi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Ch\u00faa sau khi Argentina tho\u00e1t hi\u1ec3m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/27/ngay-hom-nay-276.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (27/6). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi b\u00e1m s\u00e1t t\u1eebng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)</div>\r\n<h2>Messi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Ch\u00faa sau khi Argentina tho\u00e1t hi\u1ec3m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Messi n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng ch\u00ednh Ch\u00faa \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Argentina l\u00e1ch qua khe c\u1eeda h\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out \u1edf World Cup 2018 b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \"Albicelestes\" ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u: \"T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Ch\u00faa \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Argentina ph\u1ea3i ra v\u1ec1 s\u1edbm. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng theo c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng ni\u1ec1m vui chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\", ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Argentina chia s\u1ebb.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay, tin t\u1ee9c World Cup ng\u00e0y 276 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay, tin t\u1ee9c World Cup ng\u00e0y 276 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/Du-am-Nigeria-vs-Argentina-bang-D-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Maradona t\u1ee5t huy\u1ebft \u00e1p, kh\u00f3 th\u1edf sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Argentina</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\"C\u1eadu b\u00e9 v\u00e0ng\" Diego Maradona t\u1ecf r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00ecu v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng sau khi xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh gi\u1eefa Nigeria v\u00e0 Argentina \u0111\u00eam qua. Sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf 2-1 c\u1ee7a Argentina tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria, Maradona \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n t\u1ee5t huy\u1ebft \u00e1p. \"C\u1eadu b\u00e9 v\u00e0ng\" kh\u00f3 th\u1edf v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00ecu v\u00e0o trong ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/huyen-thoai-maradona-nhap-vien-khan-cap-sau-tran-nigeria-12-argentina-421-189721.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/huyen-thoai-maradona-nhap-vien-khan-cap-sau-tran-nigeria-12-argentina.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/huyen-thoai-maradona-nhap-vien-khan-cap-sau-tran-nigeria-12-argentina-421-189721.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Maradona nh\u1eadp vi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea9n c\u1ea5p sau tr\u1eadn Nigeria 1-2 Argentina</span><br>\r\n<span>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i 57 tu\u1ed5i gi\u01a1 ng\u00f3n tay th\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 trong c\u01a1n ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch, v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00ecu \u0111i sau b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Marcos Rojo.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Kane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1eadu thu\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">C\u00fa hat-trick \"d\u1ec5 nh\u01b0 \u0103n k\u1eb9o\" v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Panama \u0111\u01b0a Kane v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup 2018. Trong tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9, d\u00f9 Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111i ti\u1ebfp nh\u01b0ng HLV Southgate cam k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 Kane ra s\u00e2n ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 n\u00e2ng cao th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111ua v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh Lukaku c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y 276 Messi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Ch\u00faa sau khi Argentina tho\u00e1t hi\u1ec3m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y 276 Messi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Ch\u00faa sau khi Argentina tho\u00e1t hi\u1ec3m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/Tin-nong-World-Cup-2018-ngay-276-Messi-cam-on-Chua-sau-khi-Argentina-thoat-hiem-hinh-anh-2.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Ozil nguy c\u01a1 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">V\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Mesut Ozil t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 suy gi\u1ea3m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Anh ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau tr\u1eadn thua Mexico. Ozil \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. Theo d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0110\u1ee9c, g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng s\u1ed1 10 v\u1eabn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00eam nay.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-joachim-low-noi-gi-ve-quyet-dinh-loai-bo-mesut-ozil-421-189410.html\">HLV Joachim Low n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf Mesut Ozil?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>World Cup s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Adidas \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1ec1 \"Telstar Mechta\", qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u1edf World Cup n\u0103m nay. Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \"Telstar 18\" s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, \"Telstar Mechta\" \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u1edbi m\u00e0u \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9ng, m\u00e0 theo Adidas, l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4n vinh m\u00e0u s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 gia t\u0103ng \"s\u1ee9c n\u00f3ng\" cho nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"629","checkdouble":"189725"},{"date":"07:11 27/06","title":"To\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh m\u00e0n \"tho\u00e1t ch\u1ebft\" ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Argentina","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/toan-canh-man-thoat-chet-ngoan-muc-cua-argentina.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1eeb ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i khi Nigeria g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m 11m, Argentina nh\u01b0 \"s\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i\" khi Rojo ghi b\u00e0n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn c\u00f9ng gi\u1edd, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i Iceland b\u1ecb Croatia \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i. </h2><div style=\"text - align:center; width: 100 %; padding: 20px 0; \"><video data-dashjs-player=\"\" src=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/DRM/201806/273867/stream.mpd\" controls=\"\"></video></div>\r\n<div style=\"text - align:center; width: 100 %; padding: 20px 0; \"><video data-dashjs-player=\"\" src=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/DRM/201806/273864/stream.mpd\" controls=\"\"></video></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina 1-2 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina 1-2 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/Tong-hop-hinh-anh-tran-Nigeria-vs-Argentina-1-2-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Argentina d\u1eabn 1-0:</strong> Ph\u00fat 14 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1eabu gi\u1eefa Nigeria v\u00e0 Argentina, Messi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Banega v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tinh t\u1ebf, \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a anh v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, Argentina \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng B v\u1edbi 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m, Iceland 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 Nigeria 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean, th\u00ec Argentina v\u00e0 Croatia s\u1ebd \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nigeria go hoa 1-1\" title=\"Nigeria g\u1ee1 ho\u00e0 1-1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/2.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Nigeria g\u1ee1 ho\u00e0 1-1: </strong>Ph\u00fat 51, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Victor Moses g\u1ee1 ho\u00e0 cho Nigeria tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m, s\u1ebd s\u00e1nh b\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f9ng Croatia v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng sau.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Croatia dan Iceland 1-0\" title=\"Croatia d\u1eabn Iceland 1-0\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/070452-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Croatia d\u1eabn Iceland 1-0: </strong>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Nigeria c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 khi Badelj c\u1ee7a Croatia ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Iceland. Croatia l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang c\u00f3 9 \u0111i\u1ec3m, trong khi Iceland b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y xu\u1ed1ng b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Iceland go hoa 1-1\" title=\"Iceland g\u1ee1 ho\u00e0 1-1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/4.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Iceland g\u1ee1 ho\u00e0 1-1:</strong> Gilfy Sigurdsson g\u1ee1 ho\u00e0 cho Iceland tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu Iceland th\u1eafng 2-1 v\u00e0 Argentina ghi th\u00eam 1 b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ea3o s\u1ebd \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Iceland l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ghi th\u00eam 1 b\u00e0n n\u1eefa v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u nguy\u1ec7n Nigeria c\u0169ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"VAR cuu Argentina\" title=\"VAR c\u1ee9u Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/5.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>VAR c\u1ee9u Argentina:</strong> Ph\u00fat 77, Nigeria su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n khi Marcos Rojo \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m. Tham kh\u1ea3o VAR, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i kh\u00f4ng cho Nigeria h\u01b0\u1edfng penalty. N\u1ebfu Nigeria ghi b\u00e0n trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u coi nh\u01b0 ng\u00e3 ng\u0169 khi Messi c\u00f9ng Argentina b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m, Iceland th\u1ee9 3 v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marcos Rojo Leo Messi\" title=\"Marcos Rojo Leo Messi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/diem-nhan-du-am-nigeria-vs-argentina.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Rojo ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh</strong>: Marcos Rojo v\u1edbi c\u00fa s\u00fat trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-1 cho Argentina. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong n\u1ebfu k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean v\u00e0 Iceland v\u1eabn ho\u00e0 Croatia. N\u1ebfu Iceland ghi th\u00eam b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn Croatia 2-1, Argentina v\u1eabn s\u1ebd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Perisic dua Croatia dan 2-1\" title=\"Perisic \u0111\u01b0a Croatia d\u1eabn 2-1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/7.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Perisic \u0111\u01b0a Croatia d\u1eabn 2-1: </strong>Nh\u01b0ng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra. Iceland t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. Ivan Perisic ghi b\u00e0n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00e0o ph\u00fat 90, \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 cho Croatia. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 b\u0103ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Con voi Argentina, ho co 4 diem sau khi gianh chien thang truoc Nigeria, qua do dung nhi bang. Doi bong chau Phi thua tran nen chi co 3 diem. Ket qua nay giup Argentina lot vao vong dau loai truc tiep voi tu cach doi nhi bang D va se gap Phap tai von\" title=\"C\u00f2n v\u1edbi Argentina, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau khi gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria, qua \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi thua tr\u1eadn n\u00ean ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y gi\u00fap Argentina l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng D v\u00e0 s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i v\u00f2n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/8.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u00f2n v\u1edbi Argentina, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau khi gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria,  qua \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi thua tr\u1eadn n\u00ean ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.  K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y gi\u00fap Argentina l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch  \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng D v\u00e0 s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bang xep hang chung cuoc tai bang D\" title=\"B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng chung cu\u1ed9c t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/bang-D.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng chung cu\u1ed9c t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n quan t\u00e2m\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/vi-sao-trong-tai-cakir-khong-thoi-11m-cho-nigeria-du-ap-dung-var-421-189703.html\">V\u00ec sao tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Cakir kh\u00f4ng th\u1ed5i 11m cho Nigeria d\u00f9 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng VAR?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/argentina-nhoc-nhan-vuot-ai-nigeria-vui-the-la-du-roi-421-189701.html\">Argentina nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t \u1ea3i Nigeria: Vui th\u1ebf l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 r\u1ed3i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-argentina-nghi-sao-ve-man-vuot-cua-tu-kich-tinh-421-189694.html\">HLV Argentina ngh\u0129 sao v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n v\u01b0\u1ee3t c\u1eeda t\u1eed k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-nigeria-12-argentina-421-189693.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Nigeria 1-2 Argentina</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/messi-dua-argentina-vuot-qua-cua-tu-luon-la-mot-ngoi-sao-sang-choi-hon-tat-ca-421-189690.html\">Messi \u0111\u01b0a Argentina v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1eeda t\u1eed: Lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng ch\u00f3i h\u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thong-ke-gay-soc-tran-nigeria-12-argentina-421-189683.html\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c tr\u1eadn Nigeria 1-2 Argentina</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bi-argentina-loai-day-cay-dang-hlv-nigeria-noi-gi-421-189684.html\">B\u1ecb Argentina lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7y cay \u0111\u1eafng HLV Nigeria n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/messi-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-nghet-tho-truoc-nigeria-421-189686.html\">Messi n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"628","checkdouble":"189696"},{"date":"07:16 27/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh: D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2016, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3 xong m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 \u0111\u00e3 vay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh b\u1eb1ng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eadm 4-0 t\u1ea1i Pleiku. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>1. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng V\u0103n To\u00e0n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn mang t\u00ean Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 V-League, tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 s\u1edbm c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u1edd t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00fang t\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c nh\u01b0 c\u1ed7 xe \u0111ua c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c 1 \u0111\u00e3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n s\u1ef1 \u0111eo b\u00e1m c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u0103ng xu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho HAGL.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/1528076018_4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u0103n To\u00e0n l\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t trong tr\u1eadn&nbsp;</em><i>HAGL 4-0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</i></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00cdt ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, V\u0103n To\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi bu\u1ed9c D\u01b0\u01a1ng Thanh H\u00e0o ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf r\u1eddi s\u00e2n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01a1i h\u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi, V\u0103n To\u00e0n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa. Qua \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean BXH V-League 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, V\u0103n To\u00e0n ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a m\u1edf ra chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho HAGL \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 anh, ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc &lsquo;G\u1ed7&rsquo; \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>2. C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi pha s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng ghim th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi CLB Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 s\u01b0u t\u1eadp cho m\u00ecnh 7 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u1ed9i ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t V-League, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 c\u00f2n k\u00e9m xa th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Oseni (CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i) nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cong Phuong HAGL vs Than Quang Ninh\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng HAGL vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/1523280831_5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn HAGL vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i HAGL c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tin vui v\u1edbi HLV Park Hang Seo khi m\u00e0 trong th\u00e2m t\u00e2m \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t tin t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 v\u00e0 \u0111ang k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 v\u00e0 xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 AFF Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. Ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111i d\u1ec5, kh\u00f3 v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, CLB HAGL \u0111ang duy tr\u00ec th\u00e0nh t\u00edch 4 th\u1eafng, 2 h\u00f2a v\u00e0 1 b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi HAGL d\u00f9 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 4-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u0103m nay. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, HAGL v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n l\u00ean cao t\u1eebng h\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng M\u1ecf v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-0 t\u1ea1i c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i s\u1ef1 quen thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n s\u00e2n b\u00e3i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a NHM, m\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed lo\u00e3ng t\u1ea1i Pleiku c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ee5t h\u01a1i khi t\u1edbi ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai thi \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL \u1edf v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y d\u00f9 h\u1ecd m\u1edbi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua HAGL tr\u00ean s\u00e2n C\u1ea9m Ph\u1ea3 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>4. HAGL \u0111ang t\u1ed1t d\u1ea7n l\u00ean v\u1edbi d\u00e0n n\u1ed9i binh<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1 ch\u1ea5p T\u00e2y \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 100% c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed9i, tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi t\u1eeb v\u00f9ng \u0110\u00f4ng B\u1eafc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 l\u1edbn, l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin. D\u00f9 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua song m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng HAGL \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i V-League, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 V\u0103n To\u00e0n hay V\u0103n Thanh v\u1eabn cho th\u1ea5y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, s\u1ef1 kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o trong c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1edbi l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, HAGL c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i V-League v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 m\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HAGL\" title=\"HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Untitled-8-3819-1530018573.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>D\u00e0n n\u1ed9i binh c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t d\u1ea7n l\u00ean qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>5. Cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1ed1p 3 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean x\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 6 tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi 23 \u0111i\u1ec3m. L\u00fac n\u00e0y kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1p 3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u1ebfp tr\u00ean HAGL l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Thanh H\u00f3a, Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a v\u00e0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng 25 \u0111i\u1ec3m, c\u00f2n H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf xa nh\u00f3m b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i t\u1edbi 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u00f9 h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea5u. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u0103m nay g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ng\u00e3 ng\u0169 khi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i song cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eabn di\u1ec5n ra r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng. L\u00fac n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 3 tr\u00ean BXH v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 chung cu\u1ed9c s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>Video: HAGL 4-0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh&nbsp;(V\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018)</em></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/26/HAGL-4-0-Quang-Ninh.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/hagl-vs-quang-ninh-vong-16-vleague-2018-372-189604.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/ket-qua-hagl-vs-quang-ninh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/hagl-vs-quang-ninh-vong-16-vleague-2018-372-189604.html\">HAGL 4-0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh (KT): Si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n</span><br>\r\nCLB ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng ngo\u1ea1i binh v\u00e0 to\u00e0n h\u00e0ng c\u00e2y nh\u00e0 l\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1eddn \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed,...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"627","checkdouble":"189697"},{"date":"07:21 27/06","title":"HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110T Argentina \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ee1 \u00f2a c\u1ea3m x\u00fac sau khi Marcos Rojo ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Nigeria \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i s\u1edbm qu\u00ean \u0111i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018, \u0110T Argentina \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria. Messi sau m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 cho &lsquo;nh\u1eefng v\u0169 c\u00f4ng Tango&rsquo; ch\u1ec9 15 ph\u00fat sau khi b\u00f3ng l\u0103n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean sau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft \u0111\u00f3, \u0110T Argentina l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n ch\u00f9ng xu\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 51. Trong t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i&nbsp;ghi th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Argentina \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00e0n l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau c\u00fa ra ch\u00e2n c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Rojo trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">2-1 l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng D. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft h\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1edbi \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung l\u1edbn h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>T\u00ecm l\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i cho b\u00e0i to\u00e1n &ldquo;c\u00f4ng c\u00f9n, th\u1ee7 k\u00e9m&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau nh\u1eefng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1, 3-4-3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland v\u00e0 Croatia, Argentina \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt 4-4-2 c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n v\u1edbi c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Lionel Mess - Gonzalo Higuian trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nigeria. Trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 n\u00e0y, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 nh\u00f4 cao tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, Messi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 s\u00fat tung l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ngay trong hi\u1ec7p 1. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc l\u00f3e s\u00e1ng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a M10 \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0110T Argentina \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 theo k\u00e8m c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nigeria v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Argentina 2-1 Nigeria Vui th\u1ebf l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 r\u1ed3i  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Argentina 2-1 Nigeria Vui th\u1ebf l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 r\u1ed3i  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/073419-5.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ngo\u00e0i b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, Messi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n trong tr\u1eadn&nbsp;</em><i>Argentina 2-1 Nigeria</i></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Messi b\u1ecb phong t\u1ecfa, Higuain c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea5t di\u1ec5n. M\u1edd nh\u1ea1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn, t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Juventus m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh \u0110T Nigeria, tuy nhi\u00ean kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 \u1edf t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Nigeria, Higuain l\u1ea1i s\u00fat b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u1ecdt x\u00e0 trong s\u1ef1 nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V Argentina.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 d\u1edf, h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 Argentina c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i n\u1ed7i lo ng\u1ea1i l\u1edbn h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u00f4ng Cuneyt Cakir kh\u1eaft khe \u1edf t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Rojo \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Argentina \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 hai tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m penalty. V\u00e0 khi \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp b\u1edfi qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i khi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 La Albiceleste l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf c\u1edd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, Argentina \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 Nigeria g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t 11m sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Javier Mascherano k\u00e9o ng\u00e3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m. \u0110\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea1m n\u1ed7i qu\u00e1 non n\u1edbt v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 34 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 Mascherano. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4n ngoan h\u01a1n, ng\u00f4i sao t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Barcelona c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 kh\u1ecfi ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n thua tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f3m l\u1ea1i Argentina v\u1eabn b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i khi g\u1eb7p d\u00e0n sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u1ed1n \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-argentina-vs-nigeria-461-189678.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/Ket-qua-Nigeria-vs-Argentina-tran-dau-bang-D-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh-3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-argentina-vs-nigeria-461-189678.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Nigeria 1-2 Argentina (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nMessi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng qua khe c\u1eeda h\u1eb9p sau 90 ph\u00fat ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf. Messi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u01b0ng Moses g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m. Cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Argentina may m\u1eafn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>V\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 m\u1edbi<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Argentina \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia. Nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia nh\u01b0 Willy Caballero, Aguero, Salvio, Acuna,&hellip; \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e0y l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Franco Armani, Marcos Rojo v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Ever Banega, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u00edt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nigeria.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i vi\u1ec7c tung Banega v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Argentina thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc h\u01a1n. \u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Sevilla c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn khi tung ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n tinh t\u1ebf cho Messi l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng. Nh\u1edd ngu\u1ed3n th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o c\u00f9ng kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u00ednh chi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o t\u1ed1t, Banega \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean k\u1ebft c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Argentina l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi nhau th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t kh\u1ed1i th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t, \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 La Albiceleste v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua th\u1eed th\u00e1ch mang t\u00ean Nigeria t\u1ea1i l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ever Banega co mot tran dau an tuong\" title=\"Ever Banega c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/banega.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ever Banega c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu Ever Banega l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 x\u00f4ng x\u00e1o v\u00e0 t\u00e0i hoa th\u00ec th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh tr\u1ebb Armani&nbsp;l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p tr\u1ea7m l\u1eb7ng v\u00e0o k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 chung c\u1ee7a Argentina. Trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh Argentina thay cho Caballero, Armani \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. C\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 2 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee9u thua cho Argentina. Ri\u00eang \u1edf t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 penalty c\u1ee7a Nigeria, Armani c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ed7i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p l\u1edbn v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Argentina t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u0103m nay, Marcos Rojo&nbsp;c\u0169ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh. Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb pha b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay \u1edf cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p hai, Rojo tr\u1ea3i qua ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh c\u00f3 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 74%, 2 l\u1ea7n t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c v\u00e0 8 l\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tranh ch\u1ea5p. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Rojo ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u1edf ph\u00fat 86.&nbsp;Rojo trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Nigeria, \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 cho Argentina. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i n\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u. Rojo v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u1ee9 gi\u1eef v\u1eefng tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc &lsquo;nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh Nigeria&rsquo;, tin r\u1eb1ng Argentina ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-argentina-nghi-sao-ve-man-vuot-cua-tu-kich-tinh-421-189694.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/hlv-argentina-nghi-sao-ve-man-vuot-cua-tu-kich-tinh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-argentina-nghi-sao-ve-man-vuot-cua-tu-kich-tinh-421-189694.html\">HLV Argentina ngh\u0129 sao v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n v\u01b0\u1ee3t c\u1eeda t\u1eed k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-nigeria-12-argentina-421-189693.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-nigeria-12-argentina.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-nigeria-12-argentina-421-189693.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Nigeria 1-2 Argentina</span><br>\r\nArgentina \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nigeria 2-1 \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/messi-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-nghet-tho-truoc-nigeria-421-189686.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/messi-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-nghet-tho-truoc-nigeria.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/messi-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-nghet-tho-truoc-nigeria-421-189686.html\">Messi n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria?</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria t\u1ed1i 26/6, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Messi cho bi\u1ebft anh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c Argentina s\u1ebd c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;&#10;font-family:\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"626","checkdouble":"189698"},{"date":"07:26 27/06","title":"HLV HAGL chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/hlv-hagl-chia-se-bi-quyet-giup-hoc-tro-danh-bai-than-quang-ninh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 26/6, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. V\u00e0 HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y?</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 16 V-League di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i 26/6, CLB HAGL c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nhi\u1ec1u duy\u00ean n\u1ee3 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng 0-3, tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm 4-0.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV HAGL chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV HAGL chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Untitled-8-3819-1530018573.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV HAGL D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. &quot;H\u00f4m nay, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed ch\u01a1i d\u1ea1t bi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng cho V\u0103n To\u00e0n. Nh\u00ecn chung, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t&rdquo;, \u00f4ng Ninh t\u00e2m s\u1ef1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft m\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam: &ldquo;Sau m\u1ed7i bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng lu\u00f4n \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t n\u00ean t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. V\u1edbi 2 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3&nbsp;k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3&nbsp;t\u1ed1t s\u1eafp t\u1edbi&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i th\u00eam v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ngo\u1ea1i binh, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec3n tr\u01b0\u1edfng HAGL kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Osmar d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, c\u00f2n tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Rimario nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 6 tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi 23 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea7y s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Tam K\u1ef3 g\u1eb7p nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c HAGL th\u01b0\u1eddng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan-168-189697.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan-168-189697.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh: D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2016, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3 xong m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 \u0111\u00e3 vay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh b\u1eb1ng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eadm 4-0 t\u1ea1i Pleiku. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh-168-189698.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh-168-189698.html\">HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi tr\u1